<p><span style="color: #cc6600; font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 21px; background-color: #fffdf8;">The BedDesk attaches to your bed frame giving you a surface to use while laying in bed.</span></p>

<p><span style="color: #cc6600; font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 21px; background-color: #fffdf8;">Perfect for Skyping friends and family, watching movies, and whatever else you want!</span></p>

<p><span style="color: #cc6600; font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 21px; background-color: #fffdf8;">The versatility the BedDesk adds to your living environment is a welcome addition to any home.</span></p>

